    <section>
      <title>About Couchbase Server Editions</title>
      <p>Couchbase Server comes in two different editions: Enterprise Edition and Community Edition.
        Each edition offers different features and levels of support that might affect your
        deployment. The <xref href="https://www.couchbase.com/products/editions" scope="external"
          format="html">Couchbase Editions</xref> page provides a feature comparison of each
        edition. Couchbase Server Enterprise Edition is recommended for production environments.</p>
